# API Switching Guide

This application can be configured to use different AI providers.

## Currently Supported

- Dashscope (Alibaba Cloud)
- OpenAI (with configuration changes)

## How to Switch to OpenAI

1. Update [app/api/chat/route.ts](mdc:lite-llm-chatbot/app/api/chat/route.ts):
```typescript
const openai = new OpenAI({
  apiKey: config.openaiApiKey,
  // Remove or comment out the baseURL line
});

// And update the model name:
const response = await openai.chat.completions.create({
  model: 'gpt-3.5-turbo', // or another OpenAI model
  // other parameters remain the same
});
```

2. Ensure you have `OPENAI_API_KEY` in your `.env.local` file.

## Adding Other Providers

To add another provider:
1. Add a new API key to `config.ts`
2. Update `app/api/chat/route.ts` with the new provider details
3. Update the README with setup instructions
